: 31, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062452406470704896", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2062452406470705164", "text": "#OOTT", "time": "08:32", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 407998, "views": 9105, "likes": 7, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062452488247055104", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2062452488247054723", "text": "#OOTT", "time": "08:32", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 407998, "views": 8973, "likes": 6, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062516791050428928", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062516791050428811", "text": "We still see robust oil demand growth, we are not changing our estimates secretary general of OPEC #OOTT", "time": "12:48", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 5265, "likes": 36, "replies": 3, "retweets": 12, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062527308964019968", "url": "https://x.com/oilin60/status/2062527308964020249", "text": "OIL - BETTER THINGS TO TRADE! ….. CL open interest is actually lower since the war started, traders have withdrawn for two good reasons, you have no edge and can get blown up, at times there are ALWAYS “better things to trade”, watching never hurt anyone. #OOTT https://t.co/CngfVNqLZV", "time": "13:30", "author": "oilin60", "author_name": "60 seconds to know", "followers": 2897, "views": 592, "likes": 8, "replies": 3, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062528875335462912", "url": "https://x.com/FirstSquawk/status/2062528875335463240", "text": "SERIES OF STRIKES REPORTED ACROSS NORTHERN ISRAEL AS CROSS-BORDER HOSTILITIES ESCALATE; SECURITY ALERTS ACTIVE IN MULTIPLE AREAS.\n\n#oott", "time": "13:36", "author": "FirstSquawk", "author_name": "First Squawk", "followers": 535065, "views": 15302, "likes": 50, "replies": 3, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062530221874568960", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2062530221874569598", "text": "Demand destruction isn’t a solution. It’s a warning @glen_downs1 \n\nIf inventories aren’t drawing as fast as expected, it may mean the economy is weakening fast enough to offset part of the shortage.\n\nThat’s not bullish. It’s a different kind of problem.\n\n#OOTT #OilMarkets #Energy", "time": "13:41", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 52887, "views": 6188, "likes": 59, "replies": 7, "retweets": 14, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062561414355537920", "url": "https://x.com/SpartaCommo/status/2062561414355538412", "text": "20 million barrels in Cushing.\n\nBelow it, spreads blow out. TI Brent shifts. The Gulf Coast stops pulling crude.\n\nFULL EPISODE 🎧 https://t.co/g5JZryd6hH\n\n#oott #crudeoil #oilmarkets https://t.co/7CVFwttwKW", "time": "15:45", "author": "SpartaCommo", "author_name": "Sparta", "followers": 5968, "views": 1004, "likes": 4, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062601968166617088", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062601968166617428", "text": "Worth to be listened comments from the Saudi energy minister from the St Petersburg International Economic Forum earlier today #oott https://t.co/n85cUECwTK", "time": "18:26", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 66547, "likes": 201, "replies": 8, "retweets": 55, "quotes": 7, "bookmarks": 71, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062604319082349056", "url": "https://x.com/SheDrills/status/2062604319082348557", "text": "This perfectly sums up forward oil prices because no one knows how close the US is to peace or more violence with Iran. We’ve been gaslighted so much by DJT everyone is going numb…that’s also part of DJT’s strategy and it’s called “Trump Fatigue”. #OOTT https://t.co/dPE6WxsTXt", "time": "18:36